      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The air in those streets hangs thick and sour, smelling of stale beer and something vaguely rotten, like forgotten garbage. Shadows pool in the narrow alleys, deep and oily, hiding things you don't want to see. The few flickering streetlights cast sickly yellow pools on cracked pavement, barely pushing back the oppressive darkness that seems to cling to the brickwork. Every distant siren sounds less like help and more like a warning.",
