      "content": "that's a good start, very atmospheric. to really ground it in reality, i need to describe the people who live there or hang out on the corners. what kind of people are we seeing in these shadows? i'm looking for those specific types of characters that make the tension feel real—you know, the ones that give off that \"stay away\" vibe and contribute to the feeling of danger and decay in the area.",
